info.name: Covalent
info.description:
The Covalent API is RESTful. The API is designed around the main resources that's available through the web interface. Sample API calls are provided next to each method using cURL.

| Parameter      | Default  | Description                                                |
|----------------|----------|------------------------------------------------------------|
| quote-currency | optional | One of usd, cad, inr, eth, eur. If not specified, use usd. |
| format         | optional | One of csv, json. If not specified, use json               |

### Supported Currencies
| Quote currency | Symbol |
|----------------|--------|
| USD            | $      |
| CAD            | $      |
| EUR            | €      |
| SGD            | $      |
| INR            | ₹      |
| JPY            | ¥      |
| VND            | ₫      |
| CNY            | ¥      |
| KRW            | ₩      |
| RUB            | ₽      |
| TRY            | ₺      |
| ETH            | Ξ      |

### Supported Networks
| Network              | Type    | ChainId |
|----------------------|---------|---------|
| Ethereum             | Mainnet | 1       |
| Polygon/Matic        | Mainnet | 137     |
| Avalanche C-Chain    | Mainnet | 43114   |
| Binance Smart Chain  | Mainnet | 56      |
| Fantom Opera         | Mainnet | 250     |
| Polygon/Matic Mumbai | Testnet | 80001   |
| Fuji C-Chain         | Testnet | 43113   |
| Kovan                | Testnet | 42      |
